{
  "stem": "15396.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was always taking them out and cleaning, then putting them-- oh, he was the best actor I've ever seen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no way on Earth-- no way on Earth that he would suspicion him of doing something dishonest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, thank goodness.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody loved him, I tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they would just take you down to question you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You never knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I-- later on, I was taken to-- when I finally left, I was told by-- this Captain Dubois warned us that I'd better go back that night, not even go to my hotel.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had already-- we'd taken some sculptures-- a sculpture that I'd done and hollowed it out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put inside it a lot of secret messages that had to get out of the country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they knew that I was going to have to go, sooner or later, and probably sooner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as it turned out, it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we sealed it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then also in my trumpet, you take out part of the third valve, the extension, and they put a lot of things in that and put it back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And those are places you wouldn't expect people to investigate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then with my American passport-- I had another sort of a passport, a carte d'identite with another name too, but that I quickly destroyed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And with-- I wasn't going over the mountains because that was already closed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was just going to go-- try to go out legally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I got to the frontier and I saw that the-- the guards-- as I say, when their suits were very well pressed and all, you knew they weren't French [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were very polite-- almost clicking their heels.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
